quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nuun, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa). Kandi ndarahiye kw’ikaramu hamwe nivyo bandikisha ko"
  68,2,"No kumigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, wewe nturi umusazi"
  68,3,Mu vy’ukuri wewe urafise impembo idahera
  68,4,Kandi ntankeka wewe urafise ingeso nziza cane
  68,5,"Rero ubu vuba uzo bona, nabo nyene bazobona"
  68,6,Ni nde afise ibisazi muri mwebwe
  68,7,"Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’uwazimiye munzira yiwe, kandi irabazi cane abarongotse"
  68,8,Rero ntuba gamburukire abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri
  68,9,Bagomba yuko wo borohereza nabo bakorohererwa
  68,10,Kandi ntugamburukire uwurahira cane nawe ari mu bantu batishoboye
  68,11,Umuvuzi w’insaku agenda asasagaza urwanko mu bantu
  68,12,"Akingira imigisha nugu hemukira ibiremwa nkawe, n’uguhakana Imana yiwe"
  68,13,"Nyene\tumutima\tukomeye,\tkuri\tivyo\tvyose\tni\tnk’ikintu\tcashinguwe ahantu mugabo ntigishingurwe neza"
  68,14,Kubera yuko afise amatungo n’ibibondo
  68,15,"Mugihe\tasomewe\tamajambo\tyacu\tmatagtifu\tavuga\tati:-\taya\tniya majambo y’ububeshi bw’abantu ba kera"
  68,16,Tuzo mushira ko inkovu kw’izuru ryiwe
  68,17,"Mu vy’ukuri abo bantu tuzobaha ibibazo nkuko twashize ko ibibazo kubari bafise imirima, mugihe barahira yuko bazo kwimbura kuri iyo mirima nihashika mu gitondo"
  68,18,Kandi ntibabwiye n’umukene numwe
  68,19,Rero warashikiwe n’ivyago bivuye ku Muremyi wabo nabo basinziriye
  68,20,Uwo murima uba nk’uwahiye
  68,21,Bukeye bara hamagarana
  68,22,"Yuko\tbogenda\thakiri\tkare\tku\tmurima\twanyu\tnimwaba\tmushaka kwimbura"
  68,23,Baragiye bongorerana
  68,24,Yuko uno musi ata mukene yinjira
  68,25,"Baragenda mugitondo biyumvira yuko bafise ububasha\tbw’ukuba buza ba bakene"
  68,26,"Mugihe\tbabona\twa\tmurima\tbaciye\tbavuga\tbati:-\tntankeka\ttwebwe twazimiye"
  68,27,Canke batwankiye
  68,28,"Umwe mubagira neza yavuze ati:- mbega sinaba bwiye yuko mu garuka ku Muremyi wanyu mu musabe ikigongwe"
  68,29,"Nabo ba mwishura bati:- iteka ni ry’Umuremyi wacu, mu vy’ukuri twara hemukiye imitima yacu"
  68,30,Baca bahangana n’abandi baterana imyikomo
  68,31,"Bavuga\tbati:-\turu\tn’uruhombo\trwacu,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\ttwari\ttwararenze imbibe z’Imana"
  68,32,"Nkumbure\tUmuremyi\twacu\tazo\tduhindurira\tuwundi\tmurima\tmwiza gusumba uwu, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turiyegereje ku Muremyi wacu"
  68,33,"Uku\tniko\tbiba\tibihano\tvy’Umuremyi\twawe,\tn’ibihano\tvy’umusi w’imperuka ni bininiya cane gusumba nkiyo bobi menya"
  68,34,"Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazoba bafise ijuru rifise imigisha y’Umuremyi wabo"
  68,35,Mbega tubagire abagamburutsi nk’abononyi
  68,36,"Mbega mubaye gute, muca intahe gute"
  68,37,Canke murafise igitabu musomamwo
  68,38,Yuko muzoronka ivyo mwipfuza
  68,39,Canke murafise amasezerano kuri twebwe azoguma ho kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka yuko muzoronka ivyo mwiganzira
  68,40,"N’ubabaze muti :- ni nde muribo yofata ingwati kuri ibi vyose"
  68,41,"Canke barafise abo bacuditse hamwe, rero nibabazane abo bacuditse hamwe niba bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  68,42,"Kuri uwo musi hazoba ibihano bikaze cane, bazo hamagarwa gupfukama bashira imitwe yabo hasi, mugabo ntibazo shobora"
  68,43,"Amaso yabo azoba araba hasi, agahinda nako kabapfuke, mu vy’ukuri bahora bahamagarwa gupfukama bashire imitwe yabo hasi mugihe bari mubantu beranda"
  68,44,"Nundeke hamwe n’abahakana ibi biganiro, tuzoba kwega buhoro buhoro mubihano vyacu ku hantu batazi"
  68,45,"Ndabahaye umwanya, mu vy’ukuri ububasha bwanje bura komeye cane"
  68,46,Canke urabasaba impembo nabo bakarengerwa nayo magarama
  68,47,Canke kuribo hariho ubumenyi bw’amabanga bahawe bw’intumwa z’Imana bandika
  68,48,"Rero n’utenyenye kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntube nk’uwamizwe n’ifi, mugihe yatabaza Imana yiwe nawe ageramiwe nabi cane"
  68,49,"Iyo adashikirwa n’imigisha ivuye ku Muremyi wiwe, ntankeka yari gutabwa ku nkengera y’ikiyaga nawe atabwa ko umwikomo"
  68,50,Mugabo Umuremyi wiwe niwe yamugenye nukumugira mu bantu b’intungane
  68,51,"Nayo ba bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, baregereza kuguhuvya n’amaso yabo, mugihe bumvise ubutumwa bwawe nuguca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri uyu muntu n’umusazi"
  68,52,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ari icibutso kubantu bose